title: Grateful Dead Live at Alpine Valley Music Theatre on 1987-06-28
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket-> Sugaree, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Althea, Little Red Rooster, Bird Song, Jack Straw

Set 2

Mississippi Half Step, Women Are Smarter, Ship of Fools, Saint Of Circumstance-> Drums-> Space-> I Need A Miracle-> Morning Dew-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: Not Fade Away-> The Mighty Quinn

reviews.review_text: Very good audience recording While the first set and part of the second set are miss labeled, the whole show is there and sounds the way I heard it that afternoon. Thanks for this show and the 28th and 7-04-1990, they are a pleasure to listen to and bring back some great memories.
Thats one feisty "Jack Straw" I love the quality these mics capture. Sounds is right up front off the PA, virtually no audience. Sure the tracking is messed up. Life isnt fair, get used to it.
